      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Thanks to extensive practice with the crossbow, you gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You ignore the loading quality of crossbows with which you are proficient.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Being within 5 feet of a hostile creature doesn't impose disadvantage on your ranged attack rolls.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When you use the @action[Attack] action and attack with a one-handed weapon, you can use a bonus action to attack with a @item[hand crossbow|phb] you are holding.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
